{
  "stem": "942.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One day, we had to walk up to this brickyard from where we were living.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was quite a march, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We carried-- we carried our bundles, and we came into this big brickyard.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What did you have in your bundle?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had some clothing, and we had some food that we bought again, you know, in Kassa, you know?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so, we took some of this food with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't have much, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We only had a little bundle, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we came into this brickyard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was-- this was a huge place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were put into a big shed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think there must have been close to 2,000 people in this big shed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I know, from statistics that I read post-war, that there were 18,000 people collected in this brickyard.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you can multiply this by all the other provinces, you know, where they were collecting the Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So you can see 18,000 people living in a area like this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were living somewhere, put into these big kilns where they were burning the bricks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "All I remember is red dust all over the place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was terrible, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was no running water.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I remember the first time they were building latrines here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was a terrible sight, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, that's the first time I saw anything like this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, the smell was awful, and there was no privacy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Children were screaming.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there was a kitchen put up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And again, it comes down to that bowl of soup, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This bowl of soup becomes a real big thing, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the brickyard was fenced around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember gendarmes were guarding the brickyard, all around.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
